                    <textarea id="ans-input" class="w-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-[2rem] p-8 text-xl text-slate-200 h-64 focus:border-cyan-500 outline-none transition-all custom-scrollbar placeholder:text-slate-600" placeholder="Type your technical reasoning here..."></textarea>
